		it’s built for both speed and safety.",
	link: "/aircraft",
};

let focusText4 = {
	header: "Slashing emissions while soaring above traffic",
	description:
		"Imagine turning a 45-minute drive into a swift 10-minute flight. MostAvio's advanced eVTOL technology offers \
